			<div class="content" id="post-content-4049854">
									

<p>Hello, folks. So I have with me an article about Nobody, which is a cold post.</p>
<p>My main goal was to really dabble in kinda of a new format for Nobody. I didn't enjoy the structure of the original format.</p>
<p>Anyway, this is a tale of Nobody doing a job while taking notes on his activities. I'm not sure what others headcanon about Nobody (I know it varies), but I hope there is some enjoyment you can take out of this.</p>
<p>P.S. Lefty is a concept from the Russian branch of SCP. I feel Nobody would know Lefty since both share a similar vibe.</p>

